Hey Everyone,

I have decided to sell most of my American beauty T206s to make room for another purchase...

Unfortunitly these cards are very tough to value.. a real head scratcher... they are all over the place from $75 to $220 for a common in GD-VG condition.

I have tried my best to value them based on their condition.. please email me at [url]blunder19@aol.com[/url] if you are interested or have any questions... I am open to trading if you have Hindu SLers which are on my want list (see below)
